    image: "/imgs/projects/nomina.png",
    company: "FGJEM",
    time: "2024",
  },
  {
    title: "Pre-Complaint",
    description:
      "Development of an online pre-complaint system using Next.js (TypeScript), MySQL, and Prisma ORM. Applied Docker and CI/CD pipelines for continuous integration and deployment. Integrated automated workflows with GitHub Actions and Nginx as a reverse proxy.",
    link: "https://fgjem.edomex.gob.mx/pre-denuncia-en-linea",
    image: "/imgs/projects/predenuncia.png",
    company: "FGJEM",
    time: "2024",
  },
  {
    title: "Wapizima Ecommerce",
    description:
      "Global e-commerce for beauty products built from scratch with Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and Redux for state management. Applied clean code practices and scalable architecture for maintainability and performance.",
    link: "https://wapizima.com/",
    image: "/imgs/projects/ecommerce.webp",
    company: "Digital Pineapple",
    time: "2022 - 2023",
  },
  {
    title: "Risk Analysis",
    description:
      "Risk assessment system for government institutions. Designed with a REST API in PHP using JWT authentication, PDF/Excel report generation, and hexagonal architecture for clean separation of business logic and infrastructure. The frontend was built with React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and NextUI.",
    link: "https://miigecem.edomex.gob.mx/cuestionario/",
    github: "https://github.com/DuarteDc/FDRPSE",
    image: "/imgs/projects/cuestionario.webp",
    company: "IGECEM",
    time: "2024",
  },
  {
    title: "Wapizima OS",
    description:
      "Online platform for beauty courses, built from scratch with Laravel 8, Livewire, Tailwind CSS, and MySQL. Implemented interactive user interfaces and scalable backend services for course management and student interaction.",
